1861e198888f4ff946f15e2215440864","tid":422102,"uid":6903,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:55:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩盡佢 如果又吾讀書 又吾玩 就對你老母吾住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個中文都讀唔掂都冇壓力啦 <br />\n樓主仲怕咩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>吾你老母</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5bcf6d88f747f64b2eef49c64943ef0974859f3f","tid":422102,"uid":6903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:55:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去到外國唔識英文嗰種無力感真係好痛苦<br />\n感覺浪費左父母好多錢<br />\n嚟到已經差唔多兩個星期 英文都係冇乜點進步<br />\n好驚真係咩都學唔成<br />\n<br />\n有冇過來人比啲意見我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港冇讀英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n完全唔足以應付，也許可以好正常咁溝通，但一到討論嘅時候就唔掂 英文底打得唔好真係唔好過去</blockquote><br />\n樓主外國邊度？"},{"pid":"24b95bd6795173bf93e383a67e77d8feaa097ba5","tid":422102,"uid":107598,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:56:39.000Z","msg":"兩個星期你諗住可以有幾大進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同啲鬼仔鬼妹挽啦"},{"pid":"b6427c3623dc9f40e217aff9db13efc6d31ab24c","tid":422102,"uid":54344,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:57:36.000Z","msg":"練囉屌，一生出黎就識講英文啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93decb2179822b8ecdc94ff1248a478422980b45","tid":422102,"uid":54344,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:58:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩個星期你諗住可以有幾大進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同啲鬼仔鬼妹挽啦</blockquote><br />\n挽乜撚姐，打個玩字有幾難？"},{"pid":"67262912d24b02fc497ebc840f4a2c07feed63ed","tid":422102,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:59:06.000Z","msg":"好明顯過去逃避啦<br />\n唔係讀書料 不如番香港 慳番啲錢黎投資<br />\n你都估計自己回唔到本"},{"pid":"07008bd3d087b910079d6ab1540ca71f3691229e","tid":422102,"uid":30249,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好明顯過去逃避啦<br />\n唔係讀書料 不如番香港 慳番啲錢黎投資<br />\n你都估計自己回唔到本</blockquote><br />\n其實你講得好啱，我本意真係諗住過嚟逃避現實<br />\n逃避本應輕輕鬆鬆hea過三年就回家<br />\n但正正就係過到嚟之後改變左自身嘅諗法 有左目標<br />\n先至會從中質疑自己 感到無助同絕感"},{"pid":"6881559e831ad9210ca3f7189854c639fc257fb2","tid":422102,"uid":30249,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:19:59.000Z","msg":"不過都好感謝巴絲打們嘅留言 無論你地嘅言論是正是負都好 我都好希望能夠將咁多位嘅言論轉化成自己嘅動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89ff5821c11d7503e5570cf5e93466a4a28cb52","tid":422102,"uid":30249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去到外國唔識英文嗰種無力感真係好痛苦<br />\n感覺浪費左父母好多錢<br />\n嚟到已經差唔多兩個星期 英文都係冇乜點進步<br />\n好驚真係咩都學唔成<br />\n<br />\n有冇過來人比啲意見我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港冇讀英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n完全唔足以應付，也許可以好正常咁溝通，但一到討論嘅時候就唔掂 英文底打得唔好真係唔好過去</blockquote><br />\n樓主外國邊度？</blockquote><br />\n英國某小鎮"},{"pid":"426d664cf7b62c59479efc0e778df8189cd32654","tid":422102,"uid":2263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:22:30.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n但唔洗驚 呢啲必經<br />\n捱過就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾得你去就信你得 盡力讀就得"},{"pid":"31eb03b435d75ac95eae442d3213d6f179021310","tid":422102,"uid":8785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:23:16.000Z","msg":"加油啦 我英文都屎到仆街"},{"pid":"023b1ef901997c9cfe7c8f37be1b3402cf90b03c","tid":422102,"uid":80570,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:32:23.000Z","msg":"利申先   過來人   已grad<br />\n<br />\n一去個陣英文屎到仆街   係連subway人地問我要乜都聽唔明個者<br />\n真係要盡玩 人地叫你去邊咩都去咩都試（尤其clubbing或者bar）<br />\n<br />\n慢慢你就發現自己冇咁屎"},{"pid":"fd0676310a1622022cb93e6518a0480e8dcba8f7","tid":422102,"uid":80570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:36:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去到外國唔識英文嗰種無力感真係好痛苦<br />\n感覺浪費左父母好多錢<br />\n嚟到已經差唔多兩個星期 英文都係冇乜點進步<br />\n好驚真係咩都學唔成<br />\n<br />\n有冇過來人比啲意見我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港冇讀英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n完全唔足以應付，也許可以好正常咁溝通，但一到討論嘅時候就唔掂 英文底打得唔好真係唔好過去</blockquote><br />\n樓主外國邊度？</blockquote><br />\n英國某小鎮</blockquote><br />\n尤其小鎮  你唔去飲野  真係冇咩機識到local fd"},{"pid":"9a911a22c94e9a0367df8425c3af6b22e134517a","tid":422102,"uid":112467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去到外國唔識英文嗰種無力感真係好痛苦<br />\n感覺浪費左父母好多錢<br />\n嚟到已經差唔多兩個星期 英文都係冇乜點進步<br />\n好驚真係咩都學唔成<br />\n<br />\n有冇過來人比啲意見我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港冇讀英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n完全唔足以應付，也許可以好正常咁溝通，但一到討論嘅時候就唔掂 英文底打得唔好真係唔好過去</blockquote><br />\n樓主外國邊度？</blockquote><br />\n英國某小鎮</blockquote><br />\n讀緊中學?"},{"pid":"d46b3405906c19cee6b055c78a8d3a70b8b3a408","tid":422102,"uid":143431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去到外國唔識英文嗰種無力感真係好痛苦<br />\n感覺浪費左父母好多錢<br />\n嚟到已經差唔多兩個星期 英文都係冇乜點進步<br />\n好驚真係咩都學唔成<br />\n<br />\n有冇過來人比啲意見我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港冇讀英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n完全唔足以應付，也許可以好正常咁溝通，但一到討論嘅時候就唔掂 英文底打得唔好真係唔好過去</blockquote><br />\n樓主外國邊度？</blockquote><br />\n英國某小鎮</blockquote><br />\n小弟也在英國某小鎮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會咁啱同一個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1928cc216d76ed181238504163f0ded3fe77cf","tid":422102,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:48:02.000Z","msg":"中文冇撚用，華狗未去過鬼佬國家唔多唔多會比人笑井底，相反鬼佬冇去過華狗國家都唔會比人笑井底，所以中文根本冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725d1456350db7be4a322ae8339a63d98532f7c3","tid":422102,"uid":123647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:53:41.000Z","msg":"最一箭雙雕一定係打工<br />\n<br />\n係咁搵d要對人既工 (最好唔好Chinatown啦)<br />\n<br />\n可能你自己或者身邊有好多人覺得難搵但我話比你知一定搵到 信我<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法可以秒速升spoken English<br />\n<br />\n我英文底好不過初頭完全溝通有問題講野lag機<br />\n<br />\n返工一個月即刻唔同曬<br />\n<br />\n當然好睇你英文底如何，不過3個月一定冇問題<br />\n<br />\n利申做call centre"},{"pid":"2af24252a40e578d0f3ac6c9c16ec2a268fa0d2b","tid":422102,"uid":15497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:59:45.000Z","msg":"兩個星期睇唔到分別架，你過多半年望返而家就見到英文好左好多"},{"pid":"2937b5ba7497288230cfa2f4ab48ac69aa5ebff6","tid":422102,"uid":112467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:02:12.000Z","msg":"英國要睇電視睇書<br />\n尤其BBC啲劇, 睇得多就識<br />\n或者去打波游水, 好快就習慣"},{"pid":"11581c3c61be439c2fba91dcfca1cf869201c350","tid":422102,"uid":147445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:04:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好明顯過去逃避啦<br />\n唔係讀書料 不如番香港 慳番啲錢黎投資<br />\n你都估計自己回唔到本</blockquote><br />\n其實你講得好啱，我本意真係諗住過嚟逃避現實<br />\n逃避本應輕輕鬆鬆hea過三年就回家<br />\n但正正就係過到嚟之後改變左自身嘅諗法 有左目標<br />\n先至會從中質疑自己 感到無助同絕感</blockquote><br />\n有目標就得，比啲信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a93e13d7d50dae3a085a0cfb3145c891855ad77","tid":422102,"uid":105245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:07:02.000Z","msg":"想當年去澳洲讀情況都同你差唔多，試下群啲鬼仔，得閒就down啲冇字幕既英文電影睇，一適應左你就會進步好快同冇咁頹，加油啦捱過先會成長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f709e07fcc4ce285fd6ea89322a426eea215ab5","tid":422102,"uid":28052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:08:37.000Z","msg":"黎左2個星期邊有咁快進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慢慢黎啦"},{"pid":"1a019c0a0434577d7412fcc8cd40144a04f4d6e9","tid":422102,"uid":84759,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:11:45.000Z","msg":"我當年出到外國都係一句嘢都聽唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但你身邊只要得你一個講中文，3個月左右就應該可以同人正常交流<br />\n<br />\n所以你要逼自己唔好咁毒，有機會就同人吹下水，d人知同明白你英文廢，多數會就你講慢d，同你一唔識就問，用心學，真係唔難<br />\n<br />\n幾個月後就無事架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c6546039a370ae88375e40e104f6fa51ed74ba","tid":422102,"uid":130493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:17:11.000Z","msg":"真心每個時期都有過渡段，慢慢黎啦，通常3個月會改善好多，至少聽方面一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然亦都要睇你係中學定大學過去，係男定係女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中學會慘少少仲要小鎮，啲人會算少接觸外國人(我指我哋)，之後都要睇佢哋人品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過至少你上堂都會要問問題點樣嘅，所以都會慢慢進步<br />\n大學就國際學生多好多，機會就同時多好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只要你敢講就得<br />\n我想講當你係一個英文環境底下，做功課做咩點樣都要用英文嘅時候，就自自然然會慢慢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾啲時間自己啦，你會睇到成果"},{"pid":"83b8399bb965bee4e5029006ef72af17131777cb","tid":422102,"uid":130493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:22:34.000Z","msg":"再開解講多句啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無嘢係真係浪費嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 您黎到外國讀書，語言進步當然理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但同時您嘅眼界都會跟住見嘅世界更多而更廣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好假咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但無理由讀書就真係淨係死讀書㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffa29fcd457d23bf31d216dbf080eee7e603913","tid":422102,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:25:13.000Z","msg":"唔洗1年包你有進步，前提唔好同班大陸人/香港人玩"},{"pid":"775ae34a0e3ec068a5b26566a67e991e361f948f","tid":422102,"uid":112483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:38:03.000Z","msg":"搭單問，想睇reddit學英文, 但係完全唔識用佢個forum, 有無人可以教下我<br />\n<br />\n係唔係唔可以好似連登咁開post, 開post一定要有片或者有圖?"},{"pid":"d35b2733ae073fcdbaf344702faa6bb12ff0f450","tid":422102,"uid":128127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:40:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問，想睇reddit學英文, 但係完全唔識用佢個forum, 有無人可以教下我<br />\n<br />\n係唔係唔可以好似連登咁開post, 開post一定要有片或者有圖?</blockquote><br />\nreddit純文字都開到po喎<br />\n不過佢啲comment又有comment真係睇到眼都殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5051c438c83d1ea0fbfbb76a51b75a6a976bf4","tid":422102,"uid":12433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問，想睇reddit學英文, 但係完全唔識用佢個forum, 有無人可以教下我<br />\n<br />\n係唔係唔可以好似連登咁開post, 開post一定要有片或者有圖?</blockquote><br />\n唔洗，只要你唔post錯sub reddit你鍾意講咩都得，上至學術討論下至打機都會有sub reddit"},{"pid":"d104c2f135abd3f1e54dd8b0e0051ca381a2f3bb","tid":422102,"uid":82268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:42:42.000Z","msg":"初初係咁，捱過左就會好舒服<br />\n比d時間磨練下自己身心<br />\n我差唔多用左4年克服home sick<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到依家番學放學做野同fd子去玩，慢慢就會知道外國既好"},{"pid":"d94cd084d90fdce214bc2ded7b50129e78b08b5b","tid":422102,"uid":12433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:43:20.000Z","msg":"有時候唔一定要群鬼，搵返ABC都得，至少無咩cultural barriers"},{"pid":"4fb03c76c8a916d4e459c6074158ba7d396ea5f4","tid":422102,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:46:47.000Z","msg":"群外國人最緊要係飲酒，唔係叫你劈酒，不過小酌幾杯 social下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"937ed7c575301c7ea9623721a24041b7de595c58","tid":422102,"uid":112483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:47:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭單問，想睇reddit學英文, 但係完全唔識用佢個forum, 有無人可以教下我<br />\n<br />\n係唔係唔可以好似連登咁開post, 開post一定要有片或者有圖?</blockquote><br />\nreddit純文字都開到po喎<br />\n不過佢啲comment又有comment真係睇到眼都殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頂, 就係咁啦, 睇到好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n有無其他介面靚d, 又多人既forum?"},{"pid":"5fae6ede554201fd4e77b0367681449ff215aa3b","tid":422102,"uid":27019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:49:23.000Z","msg":"加油呀樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b7a075400e41962f7c47bb7017b7b897e72402","tid":422102,"uid":141496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:50:29.000Z","msg":"我要轉間好d既學校 壓力都好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7c9d068e6c88d0f196a558a2fae12b08b7f251","tid":422102,"uid":101848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:52:22.000Z","msg":"兩個星期 好短時間姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f3a760fa896e205944a3cc511b01b4d2824d7e","tid":422102,"uid":740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T21:07:29.000Z","msg":"我都係啱啱3個禮拜，英文好撚差，但係做多d presentation 同組員傾下，講英文會無咁心急"},{"pid":"7dccd9aeb05c94461d116e9f7d4fc9ae8c06fecb","tid":422102,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T21:16:48.000Z","msg":"起碼半年先會有進步啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大膽d同鬼佬傾計<br />\n如果係朋友就同佢講問佢 如果你講錯 可唔可以教你講返岩"},{"pid":"a349dddd8966e19c07733bd5c16ad37478373a66","tid":422102,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T21:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aac6f52461800fc0fd91fb4c719f34fd8eab0c5","tid":422102,"uid":72179,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T21:22:36.000Z","msg":"dse 5* ielts 7.5嚟到都覺得自己英文好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇readings勁多字唔識<br />\n上堂又成日聽唔足...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f358b9c14c9832b4ff296f5f9c7a3f829df3ed6","tid":422102,"uid":112467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T21:24:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>dse 5* ielts 7.5嚟到都覺得自己英文好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇readings勁多字唔識<br />\n上堂又成日聽唔足...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nielts 7.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 無考過"},{"pid":"12c97b64672cd70da89b70aaae24012f1ce00316","tid":422102,"uid":72179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T21:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>dse 5* ielts 7.5嚟到都覺得自己英文好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇readings勁多字唔識<br />\n上堂又成日聽唔足...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nielts 7.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 無考過</blockquote><br />\n7.5好似唔算高分架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾年唔常用英文 冇時間所以冇乜溫就去咗考"},{"pid":"3a7e222afc168125714c1fb7cd23f065df616317","tid":422102,"uid":114491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T21:33:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去到外國唔識英文嗰種無力感真係好痛苦<br />\n感覺浪費左父母好多錢<br />\n嚟到已經差唔多兩個星期 英文都係冇乜點進步<br />\n好驚真係咩都學唔成<br />\n<br />\n有冇過來人比啲意見我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩個星期姐，慢慢來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇多d英文戲同多d用英文覆whatsapp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最重要係你朋友圈入面嘅人係講咩文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我去左澳洲差不多一年，英文都冇乜進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過就肯講咗好多"},{"pid":"194c97011844a81ab359fe5f1c8608ad3d43f25a","tid":422102,"uid":138019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T21:34:56.000Z","msg":"唔好同太多中國人fd <br />\n唔係嘅話只會係普通話進步<br />\n趁開學頭冇咁忙 嘗試去參與下團體運動 落下club 主動識fd<br />\nSem break 果陣可以約fd一齊去旅行 如果係英國留學 去成個歐洲都好方便 又可以見識多啲唔同地方嘅文化 盡量係呢三年見識多啲 玩多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油呀 樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf46adaa7fd491318581b24a2c9dc33ded55c94f","tid":422102,"uid":112467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T21:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>dse 5* ielts 7.5嚟到都覺得自己英文好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇readings勁多字唔識<br />\n上堂又成日聽唔足...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nielts 7.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 無考過</blockquote><br />\n7.5好似唔算高分架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾年唔常用英文 冇時間所以冇乜溫就去咗考</blockquote><br />\n無考過真係人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打讀緊大學?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\n利申 當年靠GCSE英文合格上大學</span>"},{"pid":"1600402b72ed632c3e2018d0380ea942ba42aeae","tid":422102,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T21:42:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最一箭雙雕一定係打工<br />\n<br />\n係咁搵d要對人既工 (最好唔好Chinatown啦)<br />\n<br />\n可能你自己或者身邊有好多人覺得難搵但我話比你知一定搵到 信我<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法可以秒速升spoken English<br />\n<br />\n我英文底好不過初頭完全溝通有問題講野lag機<br />\n<br />\n返工一個月即刻唔同曬<br />\n<br />\n當然好睇你英文底如何，不過3個月一定冇問題<br />\n<br />\n利申做call centre</blockquote><br />\n但係學生Visa好似唔俾打工架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd461983c233d7a96197d64ca373d15421e03a72","tid":422102,"uid":10586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T21:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>dse 5* ielts 7.5嚟到都覺得自己英文好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇readings勁多字唔識<br />\n上堂又成日聽唔足...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心 如果dse lv2去係咪仆硬街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然lv2不過平日喺香港都同鬼佬溝通到幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587a7c520d447e5e55dba756e887de611fa67c65","tid":422102,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T22:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最一箭雙雕一定係打工<br />\n<br />\n係咁搵d要對人既工 (最好唔好Chinatown啦)<br />\n<br />\n可能你自己或者身邊有好多人覺得難搵但我話比你知一定搵到 信我<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法可以秒速升spoken English<br />\n<br />\n我英文底好不過初頭完全溝通有問題講野lag機<br />\n<br />\n返工一個月即刻唔同曬<br />\n<br />\n當然好睇你英文底如何，不過3個月一定冇問題<br />\n<br />\n利申做call centre</blockquote><br />\n但係學生Visa好似唔俾打工架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你乜都唔知唔識就唔好嘈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀好你個英文班啦傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357216637657fa57e68de5214bb0da7262ec7557","tid":422102,"uid":72179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T22:07:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>dse 5* ielts 7.5嚟到都覺得自己英文好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇readings勁多字唔識<br />\n上堂又成日聽唔足...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nielts 7.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 無考過</blockquote><br />\n7.5好似唔算高分架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾年唔常用英文 冇時間所以冇乜溫就去咗考</blockquote><br />\n無考過真係人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打讀緊大學?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\n利申 當年靠GCSE英文合格上大學</span></blockquote><br />\nMaster <br />\nug喺香港讀"},{"pid":"83c4b1148ef9d27c956c8c373b371ff5a90de1da","tid":422102,"uid":72179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T22:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>dse 5* ielts 7.5嚟到都覺得自己英文好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇readings勁多字唔識<br />\n上堂又成日聽唔足...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心 如果dse lv2去係咪仆硬街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然lv2不過平日喺香港都同鬼佬溝通到幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔知其他地區/其他科啦<br />\n但我果度就international students&gt;local<br />\n所以其實個個英文都半桶水<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得其實最緊要大膽啲<br />\n唔好因為自卑而畫地自限<br />\n你肯嘗試冇人會笑你 大把人差過你<br />\n有心想進步嘅話講多啲睇多啲聽多啲<br />\n好老土 但係真"},{"pid":"0e878047545e527c0dcbe4965ac31c83c779544b","tid":422102,"uid":149406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T22:16:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩個星期你諗住可以有幾大進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同啲鬼仔鬼妹挽啦</blockquote><br />\n挽你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dea