ote><blockquote><blockquote>最一箭雙雕一定係打工<br />\n<br />\n係咁搵d要對人既工 (最好唔好Chinatown啦)<br />\n<br />\n可能你自己或者身邊有好多人覺得難搵但我話比你知一定搵到 信我<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法可以秒速升spoken English<br />\n<br />\n我英文底好不過初頭完全溝通有問題講野lag機<br />\n<br />\n返工一個月即刻唔同曬<br />\n<br />\n當然好睇你英文底如何，不過3個月一定冇問題<br />\n<br />\n利申做call centre</blockquote><br />\n但係學生Visa好似唔俾打工架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSorly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個禮拜好似有10個鐘定唔知多啲 visa有寫"},{"pid":"ae78b45b021971f712451842adc183b1c3dc2c07","tid":422102,"uid":10586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:14:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>dse 5* ielts 7.5嚟到都覺得自己英文好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇readings勁多字唔識<br />\n上堂又成日聽唔足...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心 如果dse lv2去係咪仆硬街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然lv2不過平日喺香港都同鬼佬溝通到幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔知其他地區/其他科啦<br />\n但我果度就international students&gt;local<br />\n所以其實個個英文都半桶水<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得其實最緊要大膽啲<br />\n唔好因為自卑而畫地自限<br />\n你肯嘗試冇人會笑你 大把人差過你<br />\n有心想進步嘅話講多啲睇多啲聽多啲<br />\n好老土 但係真</blockquote><br />\n溝通我反而唔怕<br />\n我最怕係如果去讀書到時成份notes成篇睇唔明<br />\n起碼溝通講嘅字冇讀書用嘅咁複雜"},{"pid":"daa4245db7a434e1b25a41294b926cbd418d1d46","tid":422102,"uid":52349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:18:32.000Z","msg":"睇多d voice tube, 識多d slang會好好多<br />\n香港學開既英文，基本上唔係for溝通"},{"pid":"0df4f6052f639c7c1da7292a5a27dc90b5a0a7a4","tid":422102,"uid":41791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:20:24.000Z","msg":"Alevel?"},{"pid":"048a82f79720e19880a3d6e211b99bedc03feb0f","tid":422102,"uid":103229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇多d voice tube, 識多d slang會好好多<br />\n香港學開既英文，基本上唔係for溝通</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽得多講得多 其實好快上手 最緊要唔好用不可一世個種態度 識好多香港人永遠覺得自己好叻/乜都識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔聽人講嘢唔理人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b279cf68269074b18422991c4f730c9fa6a8e078","tid":422102,"uid":68547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:22:05.000Z","msg":"睇你主唔主動姐，成日唔出門收埋當然唔會進步。"},{"pid":"cda3bdf302a750ad494a7c6598dfbe43f8c53f48","tid":422102,"uid":133111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:23:33.000Z","msg":"巴打讀咩科"},{"pid":"489ee6059553ea5be684d421bf9615a1aef1a2e5","tid":422102,"uid":51981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:40:12.000Z","msg":"Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎左一個月已經頂唔順assignment同唔知自己做緊乜<br />\n好彩而家識到幾個local朋友 英文好左少少<br />\n我唔知英國點但係我呢邊去下學校event 同係圖書館溫書已經有人聊講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51da8ffafc3af098c3d6f5db07175a18660625bb","tid":422102,"uid":51981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>dse 5* ielts 7.5嚟到都覺得自己英文好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇readings勁多字唔識<br />\n上堂又成日聽唔足...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心 如果dse lv2去係咪仆硬街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然lv2不過平日喺香港都同鬼佬溝通到幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔知其他地區/其他科啦<br />\n但我果度就international students&gt;local<br />\n所以其實個個英文都半桶水<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得其實最緊要大膽啲<br />\n唔好因為自卑而畫地自限<br />\n你肯嘗試冇人會笑你 大把人差過你<br />\n有心想進步嘅話講多啲睇多啲聽多啲<br />\n好老土 但係真</blockquote><br />\n呢個真<br />\n其實香港人已經好過其他國家人好多<br />\n起碼冇理解唔到既口音先<br />\n同外國人講真係冇人會笑你 最多聽唔明問你講緊咩"},{"pid":"b29c5528ea2c832257580b1de92cce3f42b94e99","tid":422102,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:44:43.000Z","msg":"有冇人英文好到已經係用英文諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd8bcdf574b9ada433a25e5e385a423e2767957","tid":422102,"uid":41791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:45:10.000Z","msg":"老實講DSE lv2 過左嚟一年。<br />\n一樣生存到一樣有local朋友，鬼妹，笑又一樣咁講。唔好話壓力，我自認讀書差考完DSE過嚟讀alevel都唔怕俾人笑，所以你都唔好放棄。<br />\n樓主加油，我樓主我係英國西南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32cbc66120bf9777893a6c09774d811de963179d","tid":422102,"uid":51981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人英文好到已經係用英文諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 英文差都可以迫自己用英文諗野"},{"pid":"869f637be38386d6d5239bdf319a479fd7988bb8","tid":422102,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:52:36.000Z","msg":"埋鬼仔堆r friend啦<br />\n你學到好多到係學校學唔到既英文架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}